rows.label: fev06_100_125_msg0001
rows.name:
Morning, folks. You're looking a bit
better-slept than yesterday.

rows.label: fev06_100_125_msg0003
rows.name:
Fan's state funeral is to be held
today, is it not?

rows.label: fev06_100_125_msg0004
rows.name:
Yeah, I think it was meant to be
happening in Seoris Plaza, right
outside the cathedral.

rows.label: fev06_100_125_msg0006
rows.name: Yes. It would be wrong for me not to.

rows.label: fev06_100_125_msg0007
rows.name:
Seoris Plaza very not far away.
Time to go! Quick-quick!
